            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">我读的是台湾联经版的复印件……那是内地还没出这本。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="660678368">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-660678368" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-660678368" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="660678368">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/56782258/">狼崽</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2013-03-30</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">牟宗三翻译较为清楚</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

    </div>
